short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Antika is a simple extension for replace video uploader's player to a simple and cool player.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Antika lets you replace players such as sendvid.com or sibnet.ru with a cleaner, simpler player (the basic video.js player).

Currently compatible sources are :
- sendvid.com
- sibnet.ru
- voe.sx
- my.mail.ru
- streamtape.com

This project is open source and available to all on GitHub.
